      <title>圭亚那总统称不会要求埃克森美孚重新谈判合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/guyana-won-t-ask-exxon-to-renegotiate-contract-president-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圭亚那总统伊尔凡·阿里周二坚决排除正式要求埃克森美孚公司重新谈判生产合同的可能性，并拒绝了该国政治反对派和活动人士的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/guyana-won-t-ask-exxon-to-renegotiate-contract-president-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 19:09:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
